{
  "id": "adv_love_2405_06_01",
  "title": "Episode 6 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏休み終了まであと五日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――5 days until the end of summer\nvacation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "芽衣を家まで送っていく",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 156.5666778325
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "それなら俺が送っていくよ\nここからだと少し遠いし\n夜道は歩いて帰るには危ないだろ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Then I'll walk you home. It's a bit\nfar from here‚ and it's dangerous to\nwalk alone at night.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 156.5666778325,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei006.m4a",
              "text": "え？　一人で帰れるから大丈夫だよ～\n夜道には慣れてるもん",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Eh? I can go home by myself‚ it's\nokay~! I'm used to walking at night!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 164.0666778325,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "俺が心配だから、送って行きたいんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm worried about you‚\nso I want to walk you home.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 170.1000111658,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei007.m4a",
              "text": "……そっか\n……うん、そういうことならお願い！\n二人で帰った方が楽しいしね！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I see… …Okay‚ if you insist!\nIt's more fun going home together\nanyway!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 173.233376034,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "芽衣を見送る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "そろそろ暗くなる時間だし\n気を付けて帰るんだぞ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It’s getting dark soon‚\nso be careful going home.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 181.933376034,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 185.833376034
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei008.m4a",
              "text": "せっかくだから{user}君も\n一緒に帰ろうよ！\n二人で帰った方が楽しいよ！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Since you're here‚ {user}-kun‚\nwhy don't you come with me!\nIt's more fun going home together!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 185.833376034,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "それもそうだな\nじゃあ、一緒に帰ろうか",
              "translations": {
                "en": "You're right. Then let's go home\ntogether.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 191.7667114019,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "告白しない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "俺に聞かれても……\n芽衣の気持ちは分からないな\n芽衣はどう思うんだ？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I don't know… I can't tell you\nwhat's in your heart‚ Mei.\nWhat do you think?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 282.1666961431,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 290.0666696946
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei017.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣は……恋かなって思ったけど\nううん……そう言われるとやっぱり\nよく分からなくなってきたよ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I thought… it was love… but umm…\nnow that you say that‚ I'm not sure\nanymore…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 290.0666696946,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei018.m4a",
              "text": "あ、ここまででいいよ\n家、すぐ近くだから\nまたね、{user}君",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ah‚ you can stop here.\nMy house is just near here.\nSee you‚ {user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 301.5333363612,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 9166.667199199992
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "ああ、またな……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yeah‚ see you…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 308.1666696946,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "（この時の選択を後悔した俺は\n後日、芽衣の家を訪れ改めて告白した）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(I regretted my choice at that time‚\nso I went to Mei's house a few days\nlater to confess again.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 312.6667103846,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 319.3000340779
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣。俺は君のことが好きだ\n俺と恋人になってくれないか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei‚ I like you.\nWill you go out with me?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 321.6333628097,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 327.866700212
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei019.m4a",
              "text": "ごめん！　あの後考えたんだけど\nやっぱり芽衣は{user}君とは\nいいお友達でいたいかな！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Sorry! I thought about it after\nthat… but Mei wants you to stay as a\ngood friend‚ {user}-kun!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 327.866700212,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "（結局、俺は芽衣に恋を教えることは\n出来なかったが、芽衣とは友達として\n残りの夏休みを過ごした）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(In the end‚ I couldn't teach Mei\nabout love‚ but I spent the rest of\nmy summer vacation with Mei as a\nfriend.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 336.2333628096,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "告白する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣。もう一度伝えたいことがあるんだ\n俺は芽衣のことが好きだ\n恋人になりたいぐらい、大好きだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei‚ there's something I want to tell\nyou again. I like you. I like you\nenough to want to be your boyfriend.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 346.2333628096,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 356.5666696944
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei020.m4a",
              "text": "……嬉しい。ありがとう\n芽衣も{user}君に\n芽衣の気持ちを伝えるね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I'm glad. Thank you. I'll tell\n{user}-kun how Mei feels too.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 356.5666696944,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei021.m4a",
              "text": "あの時は{user}君の好きが\n分かんなくてごめんなさい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm sorry I didn't understand your\nfeelings back then‚ {user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 365.8666513839,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei022.m4a",
              "text": "だけど、{user}君と\n一緒にいるうちに\n芽衣も好きとか恋が分かるようになって……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But while being with\n{user}-kun‚ Mei also learned\nabout liking someone‚ about love…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 371.0333180505,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei023.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣の今の好きは……\nあの時の{user}君の好きと\nおんなじ恋の好きだよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Now‚ the way Mei likes you… is the\nsame as the \"like\" you talked about\nback then.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 379.1666574874,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh022.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣……\n絶対に幸せにするから俺と付き合って下さい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei… I'll definitely make you happy‚\nso please go out with me.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 386.4999908207,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei024.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣も、{user}君のことが\n好き。大大だーい好き！\nこれからよろしくお願いします！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Mei likes {user}-kun too!\nI really‚ really like you!\nPlease take care of me!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 393.0666330733,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh023.m4a",
              "text": "絶対に幸せにするからな！\n恋人として、これからよろしく……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'll definitely make you happy!\nPlease take care of me as your\nboyfriend…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 403.5665984866,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei025.m4a",
              "text": "あ、でも……恋人って、付き合うって\nどうしたらいいんだろ……？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But… what do you do when you're a\ncouple? What does it mean to go\nout…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 410.066588314,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "mei",
              "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
              "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-mei026.m4a",
              "text": "芽衣、お付き合いするの初めてだから\n分かんないや……\n{user}君、教えてくれる？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "This is Mei's first time dating‚\nso I don't know… {user}-kun‚\ncan you teach me?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 418.8332549807,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2405_06_01-koh024.m4a",
              "text": "ふふっ……芽衣らしいな\n俺も詳しくはないが、もちろんだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Fufu… That sounds like you‚ Mei. I'm\nnot an expert either‚ but of course.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 427.9332549807,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_park-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.6000000398
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
